  <h1 class="entry-title">【上海招聘】 ebay 招聘 高级软件测试开发攻城狮</h1>
  <div class="info leader">
    <a class="node" href="node19">招聘</a>
     · 
    <a data-author="true" data-name="打酱油的兔子" href="../lilyandlucy">lilyandlucy</a>
     · 
    于<abbr class="timeago" title="2014-11-06T19:20:05+08:00"></abbr>发布
       · 
      最后由 <a data-name="lilyandlucy" href="../lilyandlucy">lilyandlucy</a> 于<abbr class="timeago" title="2014-11-07T11:05:17+08:00"></abbr>回复
     · 
    583次阅读
  </div>
</div>

      
      <div class="body entry-content">
        <p>（写在前面-- 我不是hr，这个贴是帮在ebay工作的朋友发哒，除了这个帖子上的东西，我只知道薪资啦~觉得自己合适又感兴趣的童鞋投简历试试哈，薪资真心不错）</p>

<p>薪资：包您满意+有股票</p>

<p>MTS 1 Software Engineer Quality Marketplaces</p>

<p>Job Location: Shanghai, China</p>

<p>Stretch yourself to go beyond traditional QE domains. For example: how to make tools/frameworks for Machine Translation which is data-driven in nature</p>

<p>Work with engineers, team leads, managers to help developing innovative testing solutions that meet market needs with respect to functionality, performance, scalability, reliability, realistic implementation schedules, and adherence to testing goals and principles</p>

<p>Help set vision for automation frameworks, continuous integration environments and test strategies across teams</p>

<p>Contribute to adopting or enhancing sophisticated, stable, internal Java automation frameworks increasing efficiency, re-usability.</p>

<p>Write automation testing in Java, Junit, Selenium and other internal Java-based automation frameworks for Frontend, SOA/Services and messaging components</p>

<p>Contribute to development and strategy for environment management, test automation admin and monitoring tools for a large scale, distributed component agile testing environment for Machine Translation</p>

<p>Prioritize and plan testing activities for the broader team including coordinated integration testing for larger projects</p>

<p>Job Requirements</p>

<p>·  Excellent problem solving skills<br>
·  BS/BA in CS or related field. MS/PhD preferred.<br>
·  Extensive experience with large horizontally scalable distributed component architectures including distributed databases and large web/soa application architectures<br>
·  Familiar with performance, flexibility and capacity implications for various distributed architectures<br>
·  Demonstrated extensive technical leadership in large cross-functional projects<br>
·  Experience developing and/or testing Soap/XML/Rest &amp; Java/JUnit and java based applications required<br>
·  Experience of continuous integration test environments (like Hudson) and automation frameworks like Selenium/WebDriver/TestNG<br>
·  Experience working on windows NT and Unix/Linux systems<br>
·  Experience with Oracle RDBMS, being able to read and write SQL queries<br>
·  Experience with scripting languages such as Perl, Python is a highly preferred.<br>
·  Planning skills to design test plans and test cases for larger multi-component products across multiple resources and parallel development tracks<br>
·  Quality Assurance background, including JUnit/Code Coverage (Emma)/Mock concepts/Static Analysis is appreciated<br>
·  Problem solving skills using programmatic solutions<br>
·  Ability to communicate effectively with developers, operations, release management<br>
·  Ability to understand and articulate how changes in technology impact customer experience, able to lead the test effort and defining strategic testing approach<br>
·  Exposure to testing applications that work on Big Data environments like Hadoop is a plus<br>
·  Experience in Agile Testing practices is a big plus</p>

<p>有意者联系小兔QQ497953254</p>
      </div>

